+ Service Principals\nwith Unity Catalog
++ Storage credential
+++_ Encapsulates SP authentication
+++_ Referenced by name in code
+++_ No credentials in notebooks
++ Workflow
+++_ Query hits UC
+++_ UC assumes SP identity
+++_ Requests temp token from Entra ID
+++_ Token passed to compute
+++_ Compute accesses storage
++ Benefits
+++_ Audit logs record access
+++_ Revoke via UC permissions
++ Note for engineers
+++_ Admins create storage credentials
+++_ Engineers use existing credentials
@endmindmap
